{"thag11.1:0.1":"Theragatha 11.1 ","thag11.1:0.2":"Ekadasakanipata ","thag11.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag11.1:0.4":"Sankiccattheragatha ","thag11.1:1.1":"“Kim tavattho vane tata, ","thag11.1:1.2":"ujjuhanova pavuse; ","thag11.1:1.3":"Verambha ramaniya te, ","thag11.1:1.4":"paviveko hi jhayinam”. ","thag11.1:2.1":"“Yatha abbhani verambho, ","thag11.1:2.2":"vato nudati pavuse; ","thag11.1:2.3":"Sanna me abhikiranti, ","thag11.1:2.4":"vivekapatisannuta. ","thag11.1:3.1":"Apandaro andasambhavo, ","thag11.1:3.2":"Sivathikaya niketacariko; ","thag11.1:3.3":"Uppadayateva me satim, ","thag11.1:3.4":"Sandehasmim viraganissitam. ","thag11.1:4.1":"Yanca anne na rakkhanti, ","thag11.1:4.2":"yo ca anne na rakkhati; ","thag11.1:4.3":"Sa ve bhikkhu sukham seti, ","thag11.1:4.4":"kamesu anapekkhava. ","thag11.1:5.1":"Acchodika puthusila, ","thag11.1:5.2":"gonangulamigayuta; ","thag11.1:5.3":"Ambusevalasanchanna, ","thag11.1:5.4":"te sela ramayanti mam. ","thag11.1:6.1":"Vasitam me arannesu, ","thag11.1:6.2":"kandarasu guhasu ca; ","thag11.1:6.3":"Senasanesu pantesu, ","thag11.1:6.4":"valamiganisevite. ","thag11.1:7.1":"‘Ime hannantu vajjhantu, ","thag11.1:7.2":"dukkham pappontu panino’; ","thag11.1:7.3":"Sankappam nabhijanami, ","thag11.1:7.4":"anariyam dosasamhitam. ","thag11.1:8.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thag11.1:8.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thag11.1:8.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thag11.1:8.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thag11.1:9.1":"Yassa catthaya pabbajito, ","thag11.1:9.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thag11.1:9.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thag11.1:9.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo. ","thag11.1:10.1":"Nabhinandami maranam, ","thag11.1:10.2":"nabhinandami jivitam; ","thag11.1:10.3":"Kalanca patikankhami, ","thag11.1:10.4":"nibbisam bhatako yatha. ","thag11.1:11.1":"Nabhinandami maranam, ","thag11.1:11.2":"nabhinandami jivitam; ","thag11.1:11.3":"Kalanca patikankhami, ","thag11.1:11.4":"sampajano patissato”ti. ","thag11.1:11.5":"… Sankicco thero … ","thag11.1:11.6":"Ekadasakanipato nitthito. ","thag11.1:12.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag11.1:12.1":"Sankiccathero ekova, ","thag11.1:12.2":"katakicco anasavo; ","thag11.1:12.3":"Ekadasanipatamhi, ","thag11.1:12.4":"gatha ekadaseva cati. "}